<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Poem on Caraway Kong</title><link>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/tags/poem/</link><description>Recent content in Poem on Caraway Kong</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/tags/poem/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>赋得亦可</title><link>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/%E8%B5%8B%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF/</link><pubDate>Fri, 27 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://demo.stack.jimmycai.com/p/%E8%B5%8B%E5%BE%97%E4%BA%A6%E5%8F%AF/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;今日与友谈及韵书今古不通，每阅辄疑，憾甚。答曰中华通韵。能普通话则通，填就完事，又不参赛，管他作甚。&lt;br&gt;
此论甚合不求甚解如小子者意，盖简而易行。细寻古韵，多合土语。然普通话横行之时，今声土语亦已式微，古声其不传可知也。不亦哀乎？此复古之论，终非一二子可为。遂顺时取便，亦合新风。试拟如下：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;center&gt;菩萨蛮&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;center&gt;沾衣泥履绵绵雨，&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;洛思旅意谁堪叙。&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;路上更无人，&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;翳翳日已昏。&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;center&gt;朱弦何处觅，&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;青眼常不睇。&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;独爱泛菱洲，&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;center&gt;雩归人倚楼。&lt;/center&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>